column5: Hey all, it's snowing pretty good out there from north of Barrie to Aurora, so far the roads are ok, but they are snow covered and some are getting icy now....    Maureen

Excuse me but I think you people have misplaced some of the white stuff  Either that or a snowcone truck dumped it's load in my driveway this morning  What the heck is going on? We've had two snow falls in the same week  Would you all just inhale already
Could y'all save some of that snow stuff and send it to me next August when I really need it?
Hardly any on the ground in Downtown T.O
